    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at Tata Housing",
    "description": "We at Tata Housing are looking for an experienced Real Estate Agent based out of Varanasi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Tata Housing:\nTata Housing is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata Housing!",
